{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Prohibit the use of flashing lights by cyclists and runners on the road",
        "additional_details": "People who suffer from photo sensitive epilepsy are so happy when they get to go on the road after being a year free from any epileptic symptoms.\r\n\r\nHowever, when they start driving they have to deal with cyclists/runners who have flashing lights on their bikes and helmets.\r\n\r\nThese harsh lights could cause them to have a seizure whilst driving and have potential to cause a serious accident.\r\n\r\nI simply want to stop the use of flashing lights on the road and for just a simple light to be used instead.",
